dNM5uRum7SyWH5CVKXpkz9mFlWW2_P_y2N1dCAA8nXy-TQMC\",\"summary\":[]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"io.vertx:vertx-web-client:5.0.1 still resolves Vert.x Core with Netty 4.2.x, and the existing 5.0.0 scaffold already documents that Netty 4.2.x needs explicit unsafe-access runtime properties for Java 25 native-image runs. No extra Maven dependency or Docker service is needed for meaningful WebClient coverage; local Vert.x HttpServer-based tests are sufficient.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Ensure the generated/native test setup passes these nativeTest runtime JVM properties for 5.0.1 as well: -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true. Keep WebClient tests self-contained with an in-process Vert.x HttpServer on localhost rather than relying on external HTTP services.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Local Gradle and native-image verification remain authoritative; these properties address the known Netty 4.2.x on Java 25 native runtime access issue but do not replace metadata validation.\",\n    \"Optional Vert.x features such as OAuth2-backed authentication may require optional dependencies, but they are not necessary for meaningful core WebClient coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d6ccfc438248a04016a3eea197ef88193afc6b08d45ffd8ce\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1602, "output": 743, "cacheRead": 36352, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38697, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782508048183, "responseId": "resp_0d6ccfc438248a04016a3eea10d9288193918b3258a0f26a54"}, "toolResults": []}
